hopobject.body: Can you hear me OK? generic elimite “French and American diplomats have worked hard in recent years to rebuild the relationship that became cracked at the time of the military intervention in Iraq. Now, the revelations about wiretapping are likely to mark a setback in this process of rapprochement. And they’re also a source of embarrassment for the US Secretary of State John Kerry who’s now arrived in Paris (for talks on Syria).
